xfce4-quark-weather-plugin (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release
  * Current weather with temperature, feels-like, humidity, wind, UV, dew point
  * 24-hour hourly forecast with SVG weather icons
  * 7-day daily forecast with temperature range bars
  * Glassmorphism popup design
  * Location search via Nominatim (OpenStreetMap)
  * IP-based automatic geolocation
  * met.no free data — no API key required
  * wttr.in fallback provider
  * Right-click context menu (Refresh, Change Location, Properties, About)

 -- Quark Weather Contributors <quark-weather@example.com>  Sun, 27 Apr 2026 20:00:00 +0000
